COLOR. Exemplar probably discolored. Carapace reddish brown, darker in cephalic region (
Fig. 13A
). Labium, sternum and endites reddish brown. Chelicerae reddish brown. Legs I–III brown, darker at tarsi. The metatarsus and tarsus of leg IV are lost. Abdomen brown with dark dorsal spots (
